{"tid":2212791,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺釣魚用麵包蟲好old school","createTime":"2020-09-22T05:22:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-27T05:28:31.000Z","uid":51346,"like":60,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"d39154b2835c9db0c5eb32615387af39913283b6","tid":2212791,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T05:22:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KAs6e68.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKAs6e68.jpg&h=94e2dc15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n啲魚都食厭啦 而且睇個樣都知唔好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n識釣一定係用以下呢3種蟲釣<br />\n<br />\n1.蜈蚣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jQMiQGa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjQMiQGa.jpg&h=aa7932a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n用蜈蚣做餌 型唔使講<br />\n細魚就幫你咬實佢 唔畀佢走 鈎都唔使用<br />\n大魚成條蜈蚣吞咗就搞到佢中毒麻痹<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反抗唔到 唔使同佢鬥力都輕鬆上釣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.蠍子<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zjcNJ2s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzjcNJ2s.jpg&h=29380421&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n用蠍子做餌同用雙重鈎無分別 一樣有中毒效果<br />\n大魚一啖咬晒鈎同蠍子仲有double penetration睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.蜘蛛<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ph7YQJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPh7YQJb.jpg&h=caa38975&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蜘蛛俠唔使講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0f5e82fa3e8e5ba368de632bb3d43252eafbb4e","tid":2212791,"uid":51346,"like":67,"dislike":4,"score":63,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T05:23:24.000Z","msg":"on9當有趣"},{"pid":"72ddab7289baa30a64f08492fba404ea98784b11","tid":2212791,"uid":133,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T05:24:11.000Z","msg":"畫工有改善"},{"pid":"21a10ebe48ffc48c174bea33c185a0346da4e